But well also look at moonshot opportunities because we know we need a plan B.

node.areas_of_interest_freeform: We are interested in the next generation of RPA companies, also described as software-defined-automation as we are acutely aware of how difficult it is to implement larger providers at scale. We view Vertical SaaS as a great opportunity to partner with companies building modern tools that serve the needs of every industry in the world  often unsexy ones. Generative AI represents an exciting new paradigm that brings the marginal cost of creation and knowledge work down to almost zero.
